## Kurzgesagt Methodology Attribution

This project implements educational video production methodologies inspired by 
and based on analysis of Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell's content creation approach. 
The quantified methodology and "nihilistic optimism" philosophy are derived from 
studying their publicly available content and stated principles.

This implementation is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to 
Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell or their team. All methodology interpretations 
and implementations are original work by the Estúdio Vértice team.

Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell: https://kurzgesagt.org/

