## Educational Use and Fair Use

This project is designed for educational purposes and the advancement of 
accessible educational content creation. The methodologies implemented are 
based on publicly available information and academic research into effective 
educational video production.

Any use of this software should respect copyright laws and fair use principles
when creating derivative content.

